{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_11_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 俳優と一般人との秘密の恋",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――打ち合わせ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— On the day of the meeting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "一晩考えてやりたいことを絞ってくれた訳だが……\n本当にこれでいいんだな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You spent the whole night narrowing down what you wanted to do…\nAre you really sure about this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もう決めました。テーマは――\n「俳優と一般人との秘密の恋」です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’ve decided. The theme is—\n“A secret love with an actor”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "これが今、うちが一番してみたい恋で\n作ってみたいストーリーやって思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think this is the kind of romance I want to try the most right now‚\nand it’s the story I want to create.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。けど俳優との恋……か。アイドルにも\n置き換えられそうだけど、なんで俳優なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. A romance with an actor‚ huh… I guess it could work\nwith an idol too‚ but why specifically an actor?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.2333348592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "「アイドルとの秘密の恋」も考えとったよ？\nけど最近、演技のお仕事もするようになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did consider “a secret love with an idol‚” you know?\nBut lately I’ve been doing acting work too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちが俳優になる未来もあったんかなぁって\n思ってたからせっかくやし演じてみたくなったんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I started wondering if I might’ve had a future as an actor as well.\nSo I thought this was a good chance to try playing that role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8333348592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、うちはお母さんとお父さんが\n俳優と一般人の恋愛結婚やろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ my mom and dad had a romance like that too—\nan actor and an ordinary person getting married‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "前に馴れ初めとかいろいろ聞いててん\nいいなーって密かに憧れてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard all about how they met and everything before.\nAnd secretly‚ I really admired that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5966992205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.9666681926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……両親の恋愛話にも憧れて……か\nそれなら俳優案も納得だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… so you admired your parents’ love story too.\nIn that case‚ I can understand why you chose an actor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3333348592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "せやろ？　それに、アイドル『鈴村優』との\n秘密の恋なんて見せられたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? And besides‚ if it shows fans a secret love\nwith idol \"Yu Suzumura\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.4333358765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ファン的にはドキドキしてくれるやろけど\n「『優』はアイドルなんだから恋愛なんてしない！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ fans might get excited‚ but—\nThey’d also think‚ “Yu is an idol‚ she would never date!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "……って感情が絶対に邪魔して、純粋に楽しく\nもし恋を遊べなくなるやん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That kind of feeling would definitely get in the way‚ and\nthey wouldn’t be able to enjoy Moshikoi purely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.8666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、本物のうちと重ね過ぎないよう\n俳優で手を打つ……これこそオタクファーストや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So going with an actor to avoid overlapping too much\nwith the real me… That’s true otaku-first thinking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.7666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……ファン心理もしっかり考えてるんだな\n言わんとすることは分かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… You really are thinking about the fans’ feelings.\nI get what you mean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、テーマは決まったことだし\n今日はこれから、細かい設定を詰めていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then‚ since the theme is set—\nLet’s flesh out the detailed settings for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— A few hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "一般人と俳優との秘密の恋……\n高校生編と、大学生編との二部構成……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A secret love with an actor…\nA two-part structure: high school arc and university arc…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "高校生編のうちは、目立たないよう眼鏡をかけて\n標準語で喋る……うん、こんな感じやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the high school arc‚ I’ll wear glasses to avoid standing out\nand speak in standard Japanese… yeah‚ something like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.7333348593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さすがは優。テーマと方向性さえ固まれば\nアイデアがまとまるのもあっという間だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of you‚ Yu. Once the theme and direction are set‚\nyour ideas come together in no time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.8666681927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "現役アイドルとは言え、同人誌作家を舐めたらあかんよ\nこのぐらいちょちょいのちょいや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I may be an active idol‚ but don’t underestimate a doujin creator.\nThis is nothing—easy-peasy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.300001526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、友情出演枠にkanaさんか……\n意外だけど、これには何か理由が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ choosing Kana-san for the cameo role…\nIt’s unexpected‚ any reason for that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.4333348593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "理由は……ふふっ。ここいらでいい役を与えて\n恩を売っておくのもええかな、と思うてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason is… fufu. I thought giving her a good role here\nmight be a good chance to earn a favor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.1333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え……恩を、売る……？\nほ、本当にそんな理由で……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… earn a favor…?\nI-Is that really the reason…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.0666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.3666681927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "いややわ～、京都人の高度な冗談やって～\n単にあの人の芝居に対する向き合い方が決め手です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh come on‚ it’s a classy Kyoto-style joke~\nIt’s simply because of her attitude toward acting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
